Package soot.jimple.infoflow.river

Class ConditionalFlowSourceSinkManagerWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.infoflow.river.ConditionalFlowSourceSinkManagerWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConditionalFlowManager, IReversibleSourceSinkManager, ISourceSinkManager
    public class ConditionalFlowSourceSinkManagerWrapper
extends Object
implements IReversibleSourceSinkManager, IConditionalFlowManager
    Wraps a SourceSinkManager and only redirects calls to methods of IConditionalFlowManager to the wrapped SourceSinkManager. Provide this to the Additional Flow such that it knows the conditions but doesn't accept sources.
    Author:
    Tim Lange
